{"tid":466843,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"全球最多人用嘅OS竟然唔係Windows！","createTime":"2017-11-13T03:04:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-16T11:11:32.000Z","uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"503207b59099d2988ea030db0be37fe2a1f13c4f","tid":466843,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T03:04:12.000Z","msg":"MINIX 可以被看作是 LINUX 的基礎。只要使用 Intel 處理器，操作系統最底層都由 MINIX 控制。這種系統可以說是目前世界上用戶最多的 OS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://www.techritual.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/screendump.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.techritual.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F11%2Fscreendump.png&h=734eae0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.techritual.com/2017/11/07/138748/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.techritual.com%2F2017%2F11%2F07%2F138748%2F&d=Xs2FPd0dkpmkrhVj0JzCg5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=32147bf0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.techritual.com/2017/11/07/138748/</a></div>"},{"pid":"71bd1b5e81e3a511bd162316c376b7b0c90917e7","tid":466843,"uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T03:07:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">Google 想移除其伺服器內的MINUS OS！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\nMINIX 在他自己的 CPU 上運行著 「Ring -3」，而用戶是沒有權限進入這個系統的。用戶能夠進入的最底層的「Ring」是「Ring 0」，這一層是你的 OS 內核所在，而大多數應用都會在 「Ring 3」中運行。<br />\n雖然用戶無法進入「Ring -3」，但 MINIX 則有權限進入你的整個電腦，而這就會引發一些安全問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。Google 就正將 Intel 的管理引擎 MINIX 從他們的內部服務器中移除<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。「Ring -3」內除了文件管理，儲存驅動外，還有一個重要功能就是網頁服務器。沒錯，你的 CPU 內有一個秘密的網頁服務器，而你沒有權限進入<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，Intel 很明顯是不想讓用戶知道這點的<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。"},{"pid":"51da6820539d87303fcedc6a73999565f4ad822c","tid":466843,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T03:08:34.000Z","msg":"對於普通用戶的我們而言要怎麼辦呢？"},{"pid":"65091941b4866ca87d7c2a2598a76546099c8c5e","tid":466843,"uid":97080,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T03:09:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對於普通用戶的我們而言要怎麼辦呢？</blockquote><br />\nJohn Linux"},{"pid":"e8fe2de119d4455735b7ccb7e3873116d1f60f72","tid":466843,"uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T03:11:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>對於普通用戶的我們而言要怎麼辦呢？</blockquote><br />\nJohn Linux</blockquote><br />\nMINIX 可以被看作是 LINUX 的基礎。<span style=\"color: red;\">只要使用 Intel 處理器，操作系統最底層都由 MINIX 控制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。</span>這種系統可以說是目前世界上用戶最多的 OS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。"},{"pid":"d2f76c5a58f9bb8d930e1b2daa4e76afc8b83dd2","tid":466843,"uid":52509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T03:35:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>對於普通用戶的我們而言要怎麼辦呢？</blockquote><br />\nJohn Linux</blockquote><br />\nMINIX 可以被看作是 LINUX 的基礎。<span style=\"color: red;\">只要使用 Intel 處理器，操作系統最底層都由 MINIX 控制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。</span>這種系統可以說是目前世界上用戶最多的 OS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n開發個hkgOS"},{"pid":"d09c36d7810bbf12d0e30468dabe8fa77c69b527","tid":466843,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T03:39:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>對於普通用戶的我們而言要怎麼辦呢？</blockquote><br />\nJohn Linux</blockquote><br />\nMINIX 可以被看作是 LINUX 的